answer_count": 319}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗方称伊朗拒绝「临时停火」，特朗普威胁伊朗整个文明将消亡，拒绝停火原因是什么？美以伊三方谁最拖不起？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "路透社 7 日援引一名伊朗消息人士的话说，伊朗拒绝与美国达成「任何临时性停火」。 这名没有透露姓名的伊朗官员说，伊朗为与美国达成「持久和平」协议设定了「先决条件」，包括敌方立即停止袭击伊朗，承诺不再对伊发动袭击并赔偿伊方损失等。他说，该和平协议应允许伊朗对通过霍尔木兹海峡的船只收取费用。英媒：伊朗消息人士称伊朗拒绝「临时停火」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-480a7d58420d3632a39f41a1ded3b7ae_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024942392235614830"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI/8Oa7tKuiphGEAMaCTExOTA1NzA3MSDv6NPOBjAAOLYEQAtyEzIwMjQ5NDIzOTIyMzU2MTQ4MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1775578244.266864", "card_id": "Q_2024926428479629248", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 148}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗哈尔克岛再次遭到袭击，传出多次爆炸声，伊朗会如何回击？会封锁霍尔木兹海峡吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "总台记者当地时间 4 月 7 日自伊朗方面获悉，伊朗哈尔克岛再次遭到袭击，并传出多次爆炸声。 美军中央司令部 3 月 14 日曾表示，美军 13 日晚对伊朗哈尔克岛实施了大规模打击，岛上 90 多个军事目标被「成功打击」。美军摧毁了伊朗海军水雷储存设施、导弹储存掩体等军事目标，但「保留」了石油基础设施。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f8d725412839d21754ba255af00907f8.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024926428479629248"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI/8Oa7tKuiphGEAMaCTExOTA1NjUzMyCRy9POBjAAOLcDQAxyEzIwMjQ5MjY0Mjg0Nzk2MjkyNDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1775578244.267609", "card_id": "Q_652397760", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国父系基因有几种？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "那个代表商、周、夷、羌、百越等等各代封建王朝？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a5861a4cc66da1257e6ba91185b3d6ee_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652397760"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/8Oa7tKuiphGEAMaCTEwNzI1NDg0NCDv09SwBjAAOF9ADXIJNjUyMzk3NzYweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1775578244.268373", "card_id": "Q_1948394179483886989", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "PE 几乎是最常见的估值手段，但哪些行业根本不适合用 PE 估值？为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "PE 估值是评估股票投资价值的常用方法。PE 即市盈率，是衡量股票投资价值的重要指标，通过市值与净利润的比值，表明投资者为每股收益支付的股价倍数。理想的 PE 比值为 1，意味着一年内可收回投资成本；而 PE 为 100 则需要一百年才能收回投资。PE 的高低可以帮助投资者判断一只股票是否被高估或低估。 但 PE 并非万能，哪些行业根本不适合用 PE 估值？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-e50dae15fed77eaba44e062ce7448c8e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1948394179483886989"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI/8Oa7tKuiphGEAMaCTExNjUxMjU2OCDb8vnFBjAAONwBQA5yEzE5NDgzOTQxNzk0ODM4ODY5ODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1775578244.269060", "card_id": "Q_2024841019833802976", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 130}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗称过去一天导弹袭击以色列北部未遭拦截，以放弃北部城市承认了失败，以实际意图如何？当前战局谁站上风？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 4 月 6 日晚，伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队航空航天部队司令马吉德·穆萨维通过社交媒体表